data.description: This stylish townhouse offers the perfect blend of contemporary design and convenience, located in a sought-after neighborhood close to all amenities. Upon entering, you'll be greeted by a sleek and spacious living area, ideal for both relaxation and entertaining. The open floor plan seamlessly connects the living room to the dining area and kitchen, creating an inviting space for gatherings with friends and family. Upstairs, you'll find two well-appointed bedrooms, each offering comfort and privacy. The master bedroom boasts a large closet.  The second bedroom is perfect for guests, a home office, or a cozy retreat. This townhouse also features a full bathroom on the upper level, complete with a bathtub/shower combination and modern fixtures. Additionally, there are two half bathrooms, one on the main level and one in the basement, adding extra convenience for residents and guests alike. Conveniently located near shopping, dining, and entertainment options, this townhouse provides easy access to everything you need. Plus, with quick access to major highways and public transportation, commuting to work or exploring the town is a breeze.  Don't miss your opportunity to own this modern townhouse in a prime location – schedule a showing today! **Key Features:** - Spacious living area with open floor plan - kitchen with breakfast bar and ample cabinet space - Two well-appointed large bedrooms - Full bathroom on upper level, two half bathrooms (main level and basement) - Private deck for outdoor entertaining - Convenient location near shopping, dining, and entertainment options
